_comment1: This file contains preset parameters for the deb library.
_comment3: The parameters are in JSON format, and the values from PARENT are inherited.
_comment2: You can add your own presets here. (Need to recompile the library.)
_comment4: Refer to the documentation for details on each field.
_comment6: Optional values (Default): PARENT(Self), RANK(1), NUM_SECRET(1), GADGET_RANK(1).
